    "en": {
      "title": "Corona for Sri Lankan team player",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Angelo Mathews, all-rounder of the Sri Lankan cricket team has been diagnosed with the corona virus.",
        "Sri Lanka Cricket has confirmed that he has been diagnosed with coronavirus by a repeat antigen test.",
        "Following this he has been isolated and Sri Lanka Cricket has said that they are following the Corona protocols.",
        "He was playing in the Test series between Australia and Sri Lanka in Galle.",
        "Angelo Mathews was also in the squad when Sri Lanka batted for their first innings the day before yesterday.",
        "In this situation, Sri Lanka Cricket has informed that Oshatha Fernando has been included in the team instead of him."
      ],
